quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"Indeed, We sent this [Qur’an] down on the Night of Decree."
  97,2,"How do you know what the Night of Decree is?"
  97,3,"The Night of Decree is better than a thousand months."
  97,4,"On that night the angels and the Spirit [i.e., Gabriel] descend by their Lord’s permission with all decrees."
  97,5,"It is all peace until the break of dawn."
